David GLAUDE: I don't read german... but I would suggest not to send Chiquitas bananas. There was a comercial war between EU and US where US (with Chiquita behind) was saying that EU was protecting it's market against those banana's from US. EU actually wanted to protect the poor country of Africa, Caraibe and arround. So try to take "Made in Dignity" banana's from those country, this will make it much more politicaly informed. ;-)
